This is a firebreath NPAPI plugin project - to compile the plugin, 
download firebreath (http://firebreath.googlecode.com/files/firebreath-1.1.0.tar.bz2),
extract, and link this directory to /path/to/firebreath/projects/gpgAuthPlugin

firebreath dependencies:
cmake
libgtk2.0-dev


then cd to /path/to/firebreath/ and run `makeprep.sh`

then cd to /path/to/firebreath/build

and type `make`

Library dependencies:
    libgpgme11-dev

To compile only the gpgAuth library, cd to /path/to/firebreath/projects/gpgAuthPlugin and execute

`g++ -lgpgme -lgpg-error gpgauth.cpp -o gpgauth`

then execute ./gpgauth

